title: Ismaily whiz kid Torric Jebrin wins on Egyptian Premier League debut
text:
Sports News | 21 October 2015 21:55 CET Ismaily whiz kid Torric Jebrin wins on Egyptian Premier League debut 
Talented Ghanaian midfielder Torric Jebrin tasted victory on his Egyptian Premier League debut for Ismaily in their 2-0 win over El-Entag El-Harby on Wednesday in their season opener. 
Dervishes coach Hossam Mido handed the former Hearts of Oak whiz kid a starting berth at home.
